message.body: Is getting to you at 615 too late?
Oh no no. Thats perfectly ok :)
Okie getting to you at 615 and leaving at 435 on Sunday :D
Sorry baby. I'm having credit card troubles.

I was thinking about rehoboth beach and you sunburnt doing your old man dance, and how hard you made me laugh. I love you. I love how you make me laugh and how you make me happy. I can't wait to marry you, sir.
Hahah darling lady, that was a sensitive moment, a flash forward 60 yrs into future. I wont always be so sprightly, but i will always be madly in love with you
Also. Be proud of me. I didn't buy anything but coffee and macaroons!!! My sister, in the other hand, $600 for 3 dresses. O_O
Oof. Crazy kids. You the strong one today! Huzzah!! Take that woman home. Gonna be broked.
Oh I know. Haha. I did REALLY want a dress but I didn't buy it.
